":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c33faa5256","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（你们哪一位知道得更详细一些，补充一下。","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ae87271eed","type":"paragraph","text":"（于桂梅同学补充，当她谈到守卫报社时）","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"18325f4aa6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有多少人？","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"75b7ee4ed5","type":"paragraph","text":"于：有两千人。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4ec5933aba","type":"paragraph","text":"（康老对总理作解释）","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92a1b79de5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们都在里面？","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4fbfdfe9e1","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：他们都睡在里面，很拥挤。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c40af24bfa","type":"paragraph","text":"（杨植霖同志于二十一时三十分进入厅内）","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94fca9310d","type":"paragraph","text":"（于继续叙述，当她谈到八·一八革命派被迫用绳子捆绑下跪时）","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5077de0874","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（对江青）他们竟敢不执行八条！","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9697642533","type":"paragraph","text":"（于继续叙述，当说到八·一八革命派被押解到省委时）","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4615f5b16f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：省委？","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"573d9998a0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a246ba1ce","type":"paragraph","text":"于：由省委干部审问，审问的全是平时造反精神最强的。……我们在雪地上冻了一夜，